    "Quantum Mob/ Q3 Symbol", "language" -> "en", "paclet" -> "QuantumMob/Q3",
     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "WignerBasis[{n, s}] returns the SU(2) irreducible basis (the total \
angular momentum basis) for the system of n spins of magnitude s in an \
association, where each basis vector is given in the row-vector \
representation. WignerBasis[{n, s} -> t] returns the basis of the SU(2) \
irreducible subspace corresponding to the single total angular momentum t. \
WignerBasis[{s1, s2, ..., s n}] or WignerBasis[{s1, s2, ..., sn} -> t] \
returns the basis for spins {s1, s2, ..., sn} with each basis vector \
expressed in the ket form.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> 
